        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "SQA acceptance criteria — COU2",
        "description": "Solver must be under version control with documented release notes, regression test suite passing at >=95%, and traceable issue log. ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 meets all three criteria with documented test coverage report."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 is under formal version control with full regression suite. SQA documentation reviewed and found complete. Achieved level 3 meets the required level 3 for MRL 5 Class III device at this factor. Confidence in SQA evidence is moderate (~55%) due to limited visibility into proprietary solver internals, but documentation meets the stated acceptance criteria."
